-- MOVES-Nancy Foster elected Risk Management Association chair
-- 
-- Tue Sep 02, 2014 11:07AM EDT
-- None



Sept 2 (Reuters) - The Risk Management Association (RMA) said Nancy Foster was elected chair of the association and J. Tol Broome Jr elected vice chair, for one-year terms that began on Sept. 1.

Foster is executive vice president and chief risk officer of  Park Sterling Corp. She is a member of the RMA's executive committee, enterprise risk management council and community bank council.